{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Hawa Abdi: Many people -- 20 years for Somalia --"},{"time":4000,"text":"[were] fighting."},{"time":6000,"text":"So there was no job, no food."},{"time":10000,"text":"Children, most of them,"},{"time":12000,"text":"became very malnourished, like this."},{"time":16000,"text":"Deqo Mohamed: So as you know,"},{"time":18000,"text":"always in a civil war,"},{"time":20000,"text":"the ones affected most [are] the women and children."},{"time":23000,"text":"So our patients are women and children."},{"time":26000,"text":"And they are in our backyard."},{"time":28000,"text":"It's our home. We welcome them."},{"time":30000,"text":"That's the camp that we have in now"},{"time":33000,"text":"90,000 people,"},{"time":35000,"text":"where 75 percent of them are women and children."},{"time":38000,"text":"Pat Mitchell: And this is your hospital. This is the inside."},{"time":40000,"text":"HA: We are doing C-sections and different operations"},{"time":43000,"text":"because people need some help."},{"time":46000,"text":"There is no government to protect them."},{"time":49000,"text":"DM: Every morning we have about 400 patients,"},{"time":52000,"text":"maybe more or less."},{"time":54000,"text":"But sometimes we are only five doctors"},{"time":57000,"text":"and 16 nurses,"},{"time":59000,"text":"and we are physically getting exhausted to see all of them."},{"time":63000,"text":"But we take the severe ones,"},{"time":65000,"text":"and we reschedule the other ones the next day."},{"time":68000,"text":"It is very tough."},{"time":70000,"text":"And as you can see, it's the women who are carrying the children;"},{"time":73000,"text":"it's the women who come into the hospitals;"},{"time":75000,"text":"it's the women [are] building the houses."},{"time":77000,"text":"That's their house."},{"time":79000,"text":"And we have a school. This is our bright --"},{"time":82000,"text":"we opened [in the] last two years [an] elementary school"},{"time":85000,"text":"where we have 850 children,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and the majority are women and girls."},{"time":90000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":96000,"text":"PM: And the doctors have some very big rules"},{"time":99000,"text":"about who can get treated at the clinic."},{"time":101000,"text":"Would you explain the rules for admission?"},{"time":104000,"text":"HA: The people who are coming to us,"},{"time":106000,"text":"we are welcoming."},{"time":108000,"text":"We are sharing with them"},{"time":110000,"text":"whatever we have."},{"time":112000,"text":"But there are only two rules."},{"time":114000,"text":"First rule:"},{"time":116000,"text":"there is no clan distinguished and political division"},{"time":119000,"text":"in Somali society."},{"time":122000,"text":"[Whomever] makes those things we throw out."},{"time":125000,"text":"The second:"},{"time":127000,"text":"no man can beat his wife."},{"time":129000,"text":"If he beat,"},{"time":131000,"text":"we will put [him] in jail,"},{"time":133000,"text":"and we will call the eldest people."},{"time":136000,"text":"Until they identify this case,"},{"time":139000,"text":"we'll never release him."},{"time":141000,"text":"That's our two rules."},{"time":143000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":148000,"text":"The other thing that I have realized,"},{"time":151000,"text":"that the woman is the most strong person"},{"time":154000,"text":"all over the world."},{"time":156000,"text":"Because the last 20 years,"},{"time":158000,"text":"the Somali woman has stood up."},{"time":161000,"text":"They were the leaders,"},{"time":163000,"text":"and we are the leaders"},{"time":165000,"text":"of our community"},{"time":167000,"text":"and the hope of our future generations."},{"time":169000,"text":"We are not just the helpless"},{"time":171000,"text":"and the victims of the civil war."},{"time":173000,"text":"We can reconcile."},{"time":175000,"text":"We can do everything."},{"time":177000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":183000,"text":"DM: As my mother said, we are the future hope,"},{"time":185000,"text":"and the men are only killing in Somalia."},{"time":188000,"text":"So we came up with these two rules."},{"time":190000,"text":"In a camp with 90,000 people,"},{"time":192000,"text":"you have to come up with some rules or there is going to be some fights."},{"time":195000,"text":"So there is no clan division,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and no man can beat his wife."},{"time":199000,"text":"And we have a little storage room"},{"time":201000,"text":"where we converted a jail."},{"time":203000,"text":"So if you beat your wife, you're going to be there."},{"time":205000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":207000,"text":"So empowering the women and giving the opportunity --"},{"time":210000,"text":"we are there for them. They are not alone for this."},{"time":214000,"text":"PM: You're running a medical clinic."},{"time":216000,"text":"It brought much, much needed medical care"},{"time":219000,"text":"to people who wouldn't get it."},{"time":221000,"text":"You're also running a civil society."},{"time":223000,"text":"You've created your own rules,"},{"time":225000,"text":"in which women and children"},{"time":227000,"text":"are getting a different sense of security."},{"time":230000,"text":"Talk to me about your decision, Dr. Abdi,"},{"time":233000,"text":"and your decision, Dr. Mohamed,"},{"time":235000,"text":"to work together --"},{"time":237000,"text":"for you to become a doctor"},{"time":239000,"text":"and to work with your mother in these circumstances."},{"time":242000,"text":"HA: My age --"},{"time":244000,"text":"because I was born in 1947 --"},{"time":247000,"text":"we were having, at that time,"},{"time":249000,"text":"government, law and order."},{"time":253000,"text":"But one day, I went to the hospital --"},{"time":256000,"text":"my mother was sick --"},{"time":258000,"text":"and I saw the hospital, how they [were] treating the doctors,"},{"time":261000,"text":"how they [are] committed"},{"time":263000,"text":"to help the sick people."},{"time":266000,"text":"I admired them,"},{"time":268000,"text":"and I decided to become a doctor."},{"time":270000,"text":"My mother died, unfortunately,"},{"time":272000,"text":"when I was 12 years [old]."},{"time":274000,"text":"Then my father allowed me"},{"time":278000,"text":"to proceed [with] my hope."},{"time":281000,"text":"My mother died"},{"time":283000,"text":"in [a] gynecology complication,"},{"time":285000,"text":"so I decided to become"},{"time":287000,"text":"a gynecology specialist."},{"time":290000,"text":"That's why I became a doctor."},{"time":293000,"text":"So Dr. Deqo has to explain."},{"time":296000,"text":"DM: For me, my mother was preparing [me] when I was a child"},{"time":299000,"text":"to become a doctor, but I really didn't want to."},{"time":302000,"text":"Maybe I should become an historian,"},{"time":304000,"text":"or maybe a reporter."},{"time":306000,"text":"I loved it, but it didn't work."},{"time":308000,"text":"When the war broke out -- civil war --"},{"time":310000,"text":"I saw how my mother was helping"},{"time":312000,"text":"and how she really needed the help,"},{"time":314000,"text":"and how the care is essential to the woman"},{"time":317000,"text":"to be a woman doctor in Somalia"},{"time":319000,"text":"and help the women and children."},{"time":321000,"text":"And I thought, maybe I can be a reporter and doctor gynecologist."},{"time":324000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":326000,"text":"So I went to Russia, and my mother also,"},{"time":328000,"text":"[during the] time of [the] Soviet Union."},{"time":330000,"text":"So some of our character,"},{"time":333000,"text":"maybe we will come with a strong Soviet background of training."},{"time":337000,"text":"So that's how I decided [to do] the same."},{"time":339000,"text":"My sister was different."},{"time":341000,"text":"She's here. She's also a doctor."},{"time":343000,"text":"She graduated in Russia also."},{"time":345000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":347000,"text":"And to go back and to work with our mother"},{"time":349000,"text":"is just what we saw in the civil war --"},{"time":351000,"text":"when I was 16, and my sister was 11,"},{"time":354000,"text":"when the civil war broke out."},{"time":357000,"text":"So it was the need and the people we saw"},{"time":360000,"text":"in the early '90s --"},{"time":362000,"text":"that's what made us go back"},{"time":364000,"text":"and work for them."},{"time":367000,"text":"PM: So what is the biggest challenge"},{"time":370000,"text":"working, mother and daughter,"},{"time":372000,"text":"in such dangerous"},{"time":374000,"text":"and sometimes scary situations?"},{"time":376000,"text":"HA: Yes, I was working in a tough situation,"},{"time":380000,"text":"very dangerous."},{"time":383000,"text":"And when I saw the people who needed me,"},{"time":386000,"text":"I was staying with them to help,"},{"time":388000,"text":"because I [could] do something for them."},{"time":391000,"text":"Most people fled abroad."},{"time":395000,"text":"But I remained with those people,"},{"time":398000,"text":"and I was trying to do something --"},{"time":401000,"text":"[any] little thing I [could] do."},{"time":404000,"text":"I succeeded in my place."},{"time":407000,"text":"Now my place is 90,000 people"},{"time":411000,"text":"who are respecting each other,"},{"time":413000,"text":"who are not fighting."},{"time":416000,"text":"But we try to stand on our feet,"},{"time":420000,"text":"to do something, little things, we can for our people."},{"time":424000,"text":"And I'm thankful for my daughters."},{"time":427000,"text":"When they come to me,"},{"time":429000,"text":"they help me to treat the people,"},{"time":431000,"text":"to help."},{"time":433000,"text":"They do everything for them."},{"time":435000,"text":"They have done what I desire to do for them."},{"time":439000,"text":"PM: What's the best part"},{"time":441000,"text":"of working with your mother,"},{"time":443000,"text":"and the most challenging part for you?"},{"time":446000,"text":"DM: She's very tough; it's most challenging."},{"time":449000,"text":"She always expects us to do more."},{"time":452000,"text":"And really when you think [you] cannot do it,"},{"time":454000,"text":"she will push you, and I can do it."},{"time":456000,"text":"That's the best part."},{"time":458000,"text":"She shows us, trains us how to do"},{"time":460000,"text":"and how to be better [people]"},{"time":462000,"text":"and how to do long hours in surgery --"},{"time":464000,"text":"300 patients per day,"},{"time":467000,"text":"10, 20 surgeries,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and still you have to manage the camp --"},{"time":471000,"text":"that's how she trains us."},{"time":474000,"text":"It is not like beautiful offices here,"},{"time":476000,"text":"20 patients, you're tired."},{"time":478000,"text":"You see 300 patients, 20 surgeries"},{"time":481000,"text":"and 90,000 people to manage."},{"time":484000,"text":"PM: But you do it for good reasons."},{"time":486000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":490000,"text":"Wait. Wait."},{"time":492000,"text":"HA: Thank you."},{"time":494000,"text":"DM: Thank you."},{"time":496000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":500000,"text":"HA: Thank you very much. DM: Thank you very much."}]}]}